2. cs.SD (Software Engineering) - The paper introduces methods to evaluate the efficiency of measurement strategies, which is a common topic in software engineering.
3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper proposes several measurement strategies based on simple principles, which is a common topic in data structures and algorithms.
4. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with the measurement of networks, which is a key topic in networking and internet architecture.
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper explores the bias that different measurement strategies may induce, which is a common topic in machine learning.
